"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/731657","Department for Education","false","2017-07-03","<p>A new procurement for services to non-levy paying employers will be launched at the end of July 2017, this will set out how much funding we are making available for non-levy employers.</p><p> </p><p>Decisions on future years’ funding will be made on the basis of ongoing monitoring of employer demand, performance and budgets.</p><p> </p>","Guildford","Anne Milton",,"2017-07-03T14:59:26.863Z",,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/731657/answer","Biography information for Anne Milton","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/731657/answer",,,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/731657/answer",,,,,"60","Education","Education","2017-06-21","Apprentices: Taxation","1","House of Commons","To ask the Secretary of State for Education, if she will take steps to guarantee apprenticeship funding for non-levy paying employers in (a) 2018-19, (b) 2019-20, (c) 2020-21 and (d) 2021-22.","false","Biography information for Angela Rayner","Ashton-under-Lyne","Angela Rayner","543"
